Appendix K – Energy Consumption Simulation Assumptions

WLTP cycle simulation conducted in MATLAB/Simulink using backward‑facing model.

Vehicle parameters:

· Mass: 880 kg (Track A), 920 kg (Track B).
· Cd·Af: 0.30 / 0.33.
· fr = 0.0065.
· Drivetrain efficiency map: η_motor = 0.92 (peak), 0.85 (average over cycle).
· η_inverter = 0.97, η_gear = 0.98, η_battery = 0.96.

Cycle: WLTP Class 1 (low power) duration 1800 s, distance 23.27 km.

Result: Energy consumption 8.8 kWh/100km (Track A) → range 436 km with 38.4 kWh battery.

